 Version of the New Testament to distinguish the disciple who was chosen after the treachery of Judas to make up the twelve (Acts 1:23–26) from the evangelist <i>Matthew</i>. However, this distinction is not observed in other languages, where <i>Matthias</i> (or a version of it) is often a learned doublet existing alongside a vernacular derivative."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Mrs. Mathis had at least 2 sons with Mathis."},"et":{"–":"Surnud","–Male":"Surnud","1203–Male":"1203–Surnud","–Female":"Surnud","1203":"1203"},"fi":{"–":"Kuollut","–Male":"Kuollut","1203–Male":"1203–Kuollut","–Female":"Kuollut","1203":"1203"},"fr":{"–":"Décédée","–Male":"Décédé","1203–Male":"1203–Décédé","–Female":"Décédée","1203":"1203","lifeSummary":"Mrs. Mathis a eu au moins 2 fils avec Mathis."},"de":{"–":"Verstorben","–Male":"Verstorben","1203–Male":"1203–Verstorben","–Female":"Verstorben","1203":"1203","lifeSummary":"Mrs. Mathis hatte mit Mathis mindestens 2 Söhne."},"ht":{"–":"Desede","–Male":"Desede","1203–Male":"1203–Desede","–Female":"Desede","1203":"1203"},"hu":{"–":"elhunyt","–Male":"elhunyt","1203–Male":"1203–elhunyt","–Female":"elhunyt","1203":"1203"},"id":{"–":"Telah Meninggal","–Male":"TelahMeninggal","1203–Male":"1203–Telah Meninggal","–Female":"Telah Meninggal","1203":"1203"},"it":{"–":"Deceduta","–Male":"Deceduto","1203–Male":"1203–Deceduto","–Female":"Deceduta","1203":"1203","lifeSummary":"Mrs. Mathis lei avuto almeno 2 figli con Mathis."},"ja":{"–":"死亡","–Male":"死亡","1203–Male":"1203年–死亡","–Female":"死亡","1203":"1203年","lifeSummary":"Mrs. MathisはMathisとの間に少なくとも2人の息子をもうけた。"},"ko":{"–":"사망","–Male":"사망","1203–Male":"1203년–사망","–Female":"사망","1203":"1203년","lifeSummary":"Mrs. Mathis(은)는 Mathis(와)과 적어도 두 명의 아들을 두었다."},"lv":{"–":"mirusi","–Male":"miris","1203–Male":"1203.gads–miris","–Female":"mirusi","1203":"1203. gads"},"mg":{"–":"Maty","–Male":"Maty","1203–Male":"1203–Maty","–Female":"Maty","1203":"1203"},"ms":{"–":"Mati","–Male":"Mati","1203–Male":"1203–Mati","–Female":"Mati","1203"